text: Georges Wahler (30 August 1933 - 20 January 2008) was a French sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:2008 deaths Category:French male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of France Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Colmar
